Package: voxtype
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Depends: libportaudio2, portaudio19-dev
Recommends: ydotool
Maintainer: dragfly <dragfly@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Voice-to-text for your terminal
 voxtype captures audio from your microphone, transcribes it using
 Whisper, and types the result into the active window via ydotool.
